### Create A New Content Type [POST]

When a new content type is created **created_by** and **updated_by** fields will be populated by request user.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
        
            {"label": "Foo", "description": "Foo info"}

    + Schema

            {
                "_id": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "iunique": true,
                },
                "label": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "iunique": true,
                },
                "description": {
                    "type": "string",
                },
                "schema": {
                    "type": "dict"
                },
                "editor": {
                    "type": "dict"
                },
                "widgets_config": {
                    "type": "list",
                    "schema": {
                        "type": "dict",
                        "schema": {
                            "widget_id": {"type": "string"},
                            "is_displayed": {"type": "boolean"}
                        }
                    }
                },
                "priority": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                },
                "enabled": {
                    "type": "boolean",
                    "default": false,
                },
                "is_used": {
                    "type": "boolean",
                    "default": false,
                },
                "created_by": {"type": "string", "nullable": true},
                "updated_by": {"type": "string", "nullable": true}
            }


+ Response 201 (application/json)

+ Response 400 (application/json)

+ Response 412 (application/json)


