### Update A Content Type [PATCH]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers
    
            If-Match: {_etag}
    
    + Body

            {
                "schema": {
                    "headline": {
                        "required": false,
                        "minlength": 5
            }}}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

+ Response 403 (application/json)

## Delete A Content Type [DELETE]      

Deletes the content type by given id. A content type will fail to delete if:

 - There are templates referencing to content type
 - There are desks referencing to content type

+ Request (application/json)

        {}

+ Response 204 (application/json)

+ Response 412 (application/json)